title: Welcome To My Blog
text:
Hey all!
Going to be posting about data journalism, gadgets, TILs (Today I Learned), note taking, and videography …. really everything I am interested in.
I have kept holding off publishing my website and blog since it wasn’t perfect, but decided to embark on a learning in the open phase.
Let me know if there is anything you are interested in hearing out!
